	<h1 class="title">联合国还在吵，但 400 万人流亡的问题终于开始有了些进展 | 难民危机是怎么回事 一</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Gardiner Harris, Somini Sengupta and Anne Barnard</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-30 13:09:09 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15642/medium/15642.jpg?1443577655" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


